dcterms:description: The UbiqLog dataset consists of lifelogging data collected from 35 smartphone users over two months, utilizing various sensors such as WiFi, Location, SMS, Call, Application Usage, Bluetooth Proximity, and Activity State, totaling 9,782,222 instances.
